{
  "stem": "5559.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I felt bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because a lot of my friends, they really left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my parents wouldn't-- and my-- I was very severe punished.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, of course, when it came to 1941 when everybody and so-and-so the story goes on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later, then they saw that they should let me go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, maybe I wouldn't be alive either, because they were fighting and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, because I want to tell you this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The changes in the school was not-- the changes were on the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have, like in Germany, to wear the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't had to do that under the Romanian-- they were a little more lenient, even the Iron Guard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when they could catch up with some Jews, young, old, or so, and they could kick him in the teeth and beat him up pretty good, they did it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was danger a little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the schools, the- the teachers, the professor, already in the higher education, they were-- I mentioning before or not, they came already with the swastika, with the armband.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you had to stand up and salute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, I don't know if I should mention that thing, because we six boys, instead to stand up us and salute, you know, we stood up and-- you know-- they call it then in Romania it's not what you say, like under Hitler you has to say, heil, Hitler.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In Romania, you had to say, [ROMANIAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[ROMANIAN] means, good health, which is not a bad word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it bothered us as Jews because we are all organized to salute, you know the Roman salute like Hitler had.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So instead to say the [ROMANIAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
